# 🎮 Mario Game Clone (HTML, CSS, JavaScript & Canvas)

A nostalgic side-scrolling Mario clone built entirely with **HTML5 Canvas**, **JavaScript**, and **CSS** — no game engines, just pure code magic!  
Enjoy classic jump-and-run gameplay, pixel art animations, and interactive enemies, all rendered directly in the browser.

---

## 🌟 Live Demo

🔗 [Play the Game Now](https://shikherrrai.github.io/mario/)  
🚀 Works best on modern desktop browsers (Chrome, Firefox, Edge)

---

## ✨ Features

- 🎮 Smooth side-scrolling platform gameplay  
- 🪙 Collectible coins and scoring system  
- 🧱 Breakable bricks and ? boxes  
- 🍄 Power-ups and player growth  
- 🐢 Enemy AI and collision mechanics  
- 🎨 Retro-style pixel graphics via Canvas  
- 🎵 Audio effects for jumps, coins, and more  
- 🔁 Replayable, responsive, and lightweight

---

## 📁 Project Structure

mario/
├── index.html # Main HTML file
├── style.css # Game styling
├── game.js # Core game logic
├── assets/ # Sprites, sounds, backgrounds
├── levels/ # Level data and config
└── README.md

